window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>This is the endgame - and it's not going well. </p> <p>The battle to keep the undead tide from the walls of London is lost. Africa is a deadly hall of mirrors, leaving Alpha team riven with dissension and doubt. And the one man who might save the world is crashing to Earth half a world away. Only our greatest warriors can walk through this fire. </p> <p>Betrayal. Chaos. Courage. Cataclysm. </p>"; 
